<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-36-0406 </DOCNO><TEXT>Some aspects of coherence and orientation in ion-atom collisions involvingfew-electron systems are reviewed. As examples, 2p-excitation in H/sup+/-H, He and H, Li-He collisions and coherent excitation of H (n=2) andH (n=3) states are discussed. 32 refs.; 14 figs. Contains author index</TEXT></DOC>